{"type": "article", "id": 16046, "title": "木质伞架", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-14T07:08:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113539UIRVre96pAb02suL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t木头的产品总有一种特殊的吸引力，比如这个放伞的架子。在木板上放上长短相间的垂直木棒，伞就插在中间，既保证了伞不会倒在地上，也能从侧面直接看到，方便取拿。木棒高低不一，密集排列，就像森林中的树。这是由克罗地亚当地手工制作的，自然的浅色带来一种简洁优雅。售价 116 欧，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/hallway-rainforest-umbrella-stand/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143436pXxGrnWlAwOoEedf.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"626\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66595745\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143436jeI4aV0tbA1JdZHW.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"626\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66595745\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143437QSRGHOq23W8lX79Y.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"665\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70744681\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}